  "Description": {
    "English": "Basic <span class=\"name name-stellar\">creature bait</span>. Can be placed directly or accessed via the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).<br><br>This bait will attract creatures and cause them to yield <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Faecium</span>. Once a creature has been fed, they may be <span class=\"name name-stellar\">tamed</span> or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">farmed</span> for their produce.<br><br>Dropping bait may calm <span class=\"name name-fuel\">angry</span> creatures.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种基本<span class=\"name name-stellar\">生物诱饵</span>。可以直接放置或通过快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）使用。<br><br>这种诱饵会吸引生物并使它们产出<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>。向生物喂食后，就有机会将其<span class=\"name name-stellar\">驯化</span>或<span class=\"name name-stellar\">养殖</span>，获得收益。<br><br>诱饵还能安抚<span class=\"name name-fuel\">发怒</span>的生物。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种基本<span class=\"name name-stellar\">生物诱饵</span>。可以直接放置或通过快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）使用。<br><br>基本诱饵会吸引生物并使它们产出<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>发现特定生物的诱饵偏好。使用特定诱饵后，可采取<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高级生物行动</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "基本的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">生物誘餌</span>。可以直接置放，或是透過快捷選單（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）選擇。<br><br>這種誘餌會吸引生物，並且讓牠們分泌<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎菌</span>。餵食生物後，就有可能<span class=\"name name-stellar\">馴服</span>或<span class=\"name name-stellar\">畜牧</span>為農產品。<br><br>佈下誘餌可能可以安撫<span class=\"name name-fuel\">兇猛</span>的生物。"
  },
